179
00:13:19,550 --> 00:13:21,700
You-You know French?

180
00:13:21,700 --> 00:13:23,820
[I know a lot of things.]

181
00:13:23,820 --> 00:13:26,330
Then-Then the meaning of this is...?

182
00:13:26,330 --> 00:13:28,870
[Don't you know what the lyrics of this song mean?]

183
00:13:29,400 --> 00:13:32,690
No, my French is just everyday basics.

184
00:13:32,690 --> 00:13:35,160
As for lyrics...

185
00:13:36,380 --> 00:13:39,120
[Take your time looking it up! Goodnight.]

186
00:13:40,070 --> 00:13:43,310
Hey, don't leave! This is not what I meant!

187
00:13:44,350 --> 00:13:46,360
He went offline so quickly.

188
00:13:46,360 --> 00:13:52,260
♫ My most beloved is back in my arms ♫

189
00:13:52,260 --> 00:13:54,750
What is it? "I've..."

190
00:13:54,750 --> 00:13:56,700
Year?

191
00:13:57,360 --> 00:13:59,660
♫ One thousand one types of colors ♫

192
00:13:59,660 --> 00:14:02,600
♫ Makes my heart flutter ♫

193
00:14:02,600 --> 00:14:05,210
♫ To the rhythm of the seasons ♫

194
00:14:05,210 --> 00:14:08,310
♫ Iin time with a song ♫

195
00:14:08,310 --> 00:14:10,740
♫ Under a weeping willow tree ♫

196
00:14:10,740 --> 00:14:13,470
♫ I've dreamt of a more beautiful life ♫

197
