202
00:15:02,410 --> 00:15:04,860
[To School of Union Chamber of Parisian Couture]

203
00:15:06,700 --> 00:15:08,400
I am done.

204
00:15:08,400 --> 00:15:10,110
Are you sending it to France again?

205
00:15:10,110 --> 00:15:12,750
Please be a little more careful when packing.

206
00:15:12,750 --> 00:15:15,260
Sure thing! Don't worry.

207
00:15:15,260 --> 00:15:17,200
Thank you!

208
00:15:28,350 --> 00:15:31,390
Hello, President Tang, what is it?

209
00:15:32,310 --> 00:15:34,380
Go over right now?

210
00:15:34,380 --> 00:15:37,900
This is an exclusive employee access card. With it, you can enter and exit the Mingyuan Building at will.

211
00:15:37,900 --> 00:15:40,220
You can even come into my office.

212
00:15:40,220 --> 00:15:43,560
In the entire building, other than me,

213
00:15:43,560 --> 00:15:47,700
only you can enjoy such privileges.

214
00:15:52,000 --> 00:15:55,890
Thank you, President Tang, for your kindness. I will definitely work harder and cherish it.

215
00:15:55,890 --> 00:15:59,850
If you let me see you slack, be careful. I may take the card back.

216
00:15:59,850 --> 00:16:01,740
Yes.

217
00:16:01,740 --> 00:16:03,320
Good luck on work.

218
00:16:03,320 --> 00:16:05,840
Good luck to President Tang as well. My future

219
00:16:05,840 --> 00:16:07,580
is in your hands.

220
00:16:12,970 --> 00:16:14,970
- Come in.
- President Tang.

221
00:16:14,970 --> 00:16:18,190
I brought Miss Mo to you.

222
00:16:18,190 --> 00:16:20,830
I have revised this contract. If you have any questions,

223
00:16:20,830 --> 00:16:22,700
you can contact me any time.

224
00:16:22,700 --> 00:16:25,450
Sure, I'll relay the message.

225
00:16:26,310 --> 00:16:28,120
Oh, right.

226
00:16:29,010 --> 00:16:32,680
I have a card here. You can have it.

227
00:16:33,460 --> 00:16:37,290
Miss Mo, President Tang specially made this card for you

228
00:16:37,290 --> 00:16:40,530
so it will be more convenient for you to come in and out of Mingyuan.

229
00:16:40,530 --> 00:16:44,060
Since it's an employee card, why give it to me? I don't want it.

230
00:16:45,950 --> 00:16:48,120
Miss Mo, you should keep it.

231
00:16:48,120 --> 00:16:53,220
With this card, it'll be more convenient for you to see our President Tang.

232
00:16:53,220 --> 00:16:55,720
But I don't come often.

233
00:16:57,290 --> 00:17:02,140
Well, you don't want to always be locked out of the building. Right?

234
00:17:02,970 --> 00:17:06,610
That's true. There are a lot of mosquitoes outside.

235
00:17:06,610 --> 00:17:08,990
All right, I'll take it. Thanks.

236
00:17:08,990 --> 00:17:12,520
But don't worry, I won't come here often. Once the embroidery workshop matter is over,

237
00:17:12,520 --> 00:17:14,070
I will return the card to you.

238
00:17:14,070 --> 00:17:16,180
My thoughts exactly.

239
00:17:21,450 --> 00:17:23,760
I'll go now. Bye-bye!

240
00:17:23,760 --> 00:17:25,500
Do you need me to walk you out?

241
00:17:25,500 --> 00:17:28,000
It's okay. I know the way. I can go out by myself.

242
00:17:28,000 --> 00:17:29,730
Bye-bye.

243
00:17:36,300 --> 00:17:38,150
This Miss Mo...

244
00:17:38,150 --> 00:17:40,550
Sometimes I can’t find my way around the administrative building,

245
00:17:40,550 --> 00:17:42,860
yet she says she can find her way.

246
00:17:51,600 --> 00:17:53,660
I'm so clever.

247
00:17:53,660 --> 00:17:57,740
It's great! I also saved his WeChat.

248
00:17:57,740 --> 00:17:59,730
Don't try to compete with me for him.

249
00:18:03,850 --> 00:18:05,780
President Tang, sorry.

250
00:18:05,780 --> 00:18:09,080
- We didn't see you.
- Why aren't you more careful?

251
00:18:09,080 --> 00:18:12,120
Shouldn't you be more focused during work?

252
00:18:14,370 --> 00:18:17,590
- Go on.
- Yes, President Tang.

253
00:18:22,740 --> 00:18:25,580
Thank you, but they were just a little careless.

254
00:18:25,580 --> 00:18:27,010
They are employees of my company.

255
00:18:27,010 --> 00:18:30,580
Be careful. I might tell your boss to deduct your bonus.

256
00:18:31,320 --> 00:18:33,930
I-I didn't do anything wrong.

257
00:18:33,930 --> 00:18:36,510
My boss is different from you.

258
00:18:37,360 --> 00:18:39,310
Hitting people again?

259
00:18:40,490 --> 00:18:42,110
It's here.

260
00:19:01,380 --> 00:19:03,700
Xueling?

261
00:19:03,700 --> 00:19:07,190
Aren't you busy with "Chinese Style"?

262
00:19:07,190 --> 00:19:09,270
I am taking a break and came to have a look.

263
00:19:09,270 --> 00:19:12,450
What? Are you going to deduct my salary as the boss?

264
00:19:12,450 --> 00:19:15,430
It all depends on how your discussion with the TV station went.

265
00:19:16,580 --> 00:19:18,670
The TV station has already released the advertisements.

266
00:19:18,670 --> 00:19:21,290
We have also started the pre-launch marketing stage.

267
00:19:21,290 --> 00:19:24,620
Store sales in first-tier cities have also increased significantly.

268
00:19:24,620 --> 00:19:28,050
I can see that many consumers came after watching the event.

269
00:19:28,050 --> 00:19:30,050
That's great!

270
00:19:31,880 --> 00:19:35,430
Also... the TV station

271
00:19:35,430 --> 00:19:38,070
wants Fang Xiaoyu to be a judge.

272
00:19:39,440 --> 00:19:44,100
If they have the ability to invite him, then let them invite him.

273
00:19:44,100 --> 00:19:48,090
He, himself, is unwilling to go, but Cayman wants him to participate.

274
00:19:48,090 --> 00:19:50,330
Then let them argue amongst themselves.

275
00:19:58,520 --> 00:20:00,170
Director Fang,

276
00:20:00,930 --> 00:20:04,890
this is "Chinese Style Fashion," a competition among designers, that the TV station is hosting.

277
00:20:04,890 --> 00:20:10,020
The organizers would like to invite you to participate in the show.

278
00:20:10,020 --> 00:20:12,150
I am not interested.

279
00:20:13,530 --> 00:20:17,600
Director Fang, how about you look at the proposal first.

280
00:20:17,600 --> 00:20:21,130
The President of the Garment Association would like you to go be a judge.

281
00:20:21,130 --> 00:20:24,540
To give the younger generation some pointers and some lessons.

282
00:20:24,540 --> 00:20:28,640
I think that the other designers aren't as handsome on camera as you are.

283
00:20:28,640 --> 00:20:32,300
Besides, Cayman needs to have a public image.

284
00:20:35,820 --> 00:20:37,800
Take a look.

285
00:20:39,740 --> 00:20:41,940
[Fashion Chinese Style Proposal]

286
00:20:43,190 --> 00:20:45,570
- It is sponsored by Mingyuan?
- Yes.

287
00:20:48,370 --> 00:20:50,100
Director Fang, I think it's a good idea.

288
00:20:50,100 --> 00:20:53,300
They give the funding and we get the exposure. What a bargain.

289
00:20:53,300 --> 00:20:55,230
How is it a bargain?

290
00:20:55,230 --> 00:20:59,580
Hosting this show, they're bound to invite the big names in the industry to support it.

291
00:20:59,580 --> 00:21:04,140
In the end, don't the sponsorships and advertisements still belong to Mingyuan Fashion Group?

292
00:21:05,290 --> 00:21:08,180
Since they've invested in it, we have to let them show off a little.

293
00:21:08,180 --> 00:21:10,930
We didn't spend any money but get free advertisement.

294
00:21:10,930 --> 00:21:13,780
- Right?
- Does Cayman lack money?

295
00:21:13,780 --> 00:21:15,720
No, of course not.

296
00:21:15,720 --> 00:21:19,050
Then, why take advantage of Tang Mingxuan?

297
00:21:21,220 --> 00:21:23,270
But... President Hu has already

298
00:21:23,270 --> 00:21:26,910
asked Linda to send models for the fashion show.

299
00:21:26,910 --> 00:21:28,950
What does that have to do with me?

300
00:21:30,840 --> 00:21:35,200
Director Fang, you at least have to give the association's president face. Right?

301
00:21:35,200 --> 00:21:37,960
What is it? If I don't give him face, will he bite me?

302
00:21:37,960 --> 00:21:40,020
He won't do that.

303
00:21:40,020 --> 00:21:42,840
I just think that since you are so handsome,

304
00:21:42,840 --> 00:21:45,510
it would be a pity not to be on camera.

305
00:21:46,870 --> 00:21:49,950
Sucking up to me is useless.

306
00:21:49,950 --> 00:21:52,830
How about you have Tang Mingxuan come beg me?

307
00:21:52,830 --> 00:21:54,810
I might say yes.

308
00:22:57,390 --> 00:22:59,550
Hello, Director Fang. Are you looking for me?

309
00:22:59,550 --> 00:23:02,500
I sent you a message. Why didn't you reply?

310
00:23:02,500 --> 00:23:06,440
What? You sent me a message? Let me check.

311
00:23:10,520 --> 00:23:12,380
What's wrong with this dress?

312
00:23:12,380 --> 00:23:16,800
I'm going to test you. What do you think about this dress?

313
00:23:18,890 --> 00:23:22,740
I think... the hemline can be made higher.

314
00:23:22,740 --> 00:23:26,030
Because velvet is a fabric that tends to appear heavy.

315
00:23:26,030 --> 00:23:30,260
This way it will make the entire effect look lighter.

316
00:23:30,260 --> 00:23:33,270
Not bad! You are indeed Teacher Pan's student.

317
00:23:33,270 --> 00:23:36,160
Our ideas coincide.

318
00:23:36,160 --> 00:23:39,600
By the way, the TV station is holding a competition called "Chinese Style Fashion."

319
00:23:39,600 --> 00:23:42,800
I suggest you sign up for it immediately.

320
00:23:42,800 --> 00:23:46,320
Director Fang, I really did sign up for it.

321
00:23:46,320 --> 00:23:48,520
- Really?
- Yes.

322
00:23:49,100 --> 00:23:52,600
Then I wish you great results.

323
00:23:53,390 --> 00:23:58,000
Say... You wouldn't happen to be a judge, right?

324
00:23:58,000 --> 00:24:01,830
Didn't you insist on not "walking through the back door"? Whether I'm a judge is not important at all.
(T/N: Using connections)

325
00:24:01,830 --> 00:24:05,500
Unless you are not confident about your design.

326
00:24:06,020 --> 00:24:09,120
I was just asking. If there's nothing else, I will hang up now.

327
00:24:09,120 --> 00:24:10,750
Bye-bye.

328
00:24:15,510 --> 00:24:17,230
Li Qi!

329
00:24:17,810 --> 00:24:19,460
Li Qi!

330
00:24:20,920 --> 00:24:25,110
- Director Fang.
- Tell the TV station that I want to be a judge.

331
00:24:25,110 --> 00:24:28,540
Just cut these and we're about done.

332
00:24:28,540 --> 00:24:30,660
Sister Mo Fei.

333
00:24:30,660 --> 00:24:33,260
Do you two need help with anything?

334
00:24:34,570 --> 00:24:36,440
Help me wash the vegetables.

335
00:24:36,440 --> 00:24:38,460
All right.

336
00:24:38,460 --> 00:24:39,900
Why are you so obedient today?

337
00:24:39,900 --> 00:24:42,820
You are talking too much.

338
00:25:13,020 --> 00:25:15,550
- Is the picture all right?
- It looks good, doesn't it?

339
00:25:15,550 --> 00:25:18,590
- Yes. Can we eat now?
- Yes.

340
00:25:20,160 --> 00:25:22,060
Here.

341
00:25:25,730 --> 00:25:27,460
Lu Zhu.

342
00:25:31,490 --> 00:25:34,730
Sister Mo Fei, to be honest, I really envy you.

343
00:25:34,730 --> 00:25:35,950
Envy me for what?

344
00:25:35,950 --> 00:25:39,190
For relying on your own skills to get to France.

345
00:25:39,190 --> 00:25:41,740
Even though I grew up abroad,

346
00:25:41,740 --> 00:25:44,190
everything was arranged by my family.

347
00:25:44,190 --> 00:25:46,990
I don't have the slightest sense of accomplishment.

348
00:25:46,990 --> 00:25:48,960
I have only sent them my designs.

349
00:25:48,960 --> 00:25:51,130
Whether they accept me or not is not certain.

350
00:25:51,130 --> 00:25:53,430
No, you will certainly succeed.

351
00:25:54,030 --> 00:25:57,100
To us all being able to fulfill our dreams.

352
00:25:57,100 --> 00:25:59,860
- Cheers!
- Cheers!

353
00:26:10,130 --> 00:26:14,000
I didn't expect you to be such a good cook.

354
00:26:14,000 --> 00:26:17,440
Then, can I come here often to eat your food in the future?

355
00:26:17,440 --> 00:26:20,600
Sure, sure! Come often! Just come, no need for a reason.

356
00:26:20,600 --> 00:26:25,160
Don't you live at President Tang's home? Is the food there that bad?

357
00:26:26,230 --> 00:26:27,670
What's up with the attitude?

358
00:26:27,670 --> 00:26:31,220
Lu Zhu likes the food you made. You should be happy.

359
00:26:31,220 --> 00:26:32,780
Say "thanks."

360
00:26:32,780 --> 00:26:35,030
Thank you, Lu Zhu!

361
00:26:35,030 --> 00:26:37,220
The food at my house is not bad.

362
00:26:37,220 --> 00:26:40,130
It's just that at the dinner table,

363
00:26:40,130 --> 00:26:44,800
there is nothing to talk about with my aunt and uncle.

364
00:26:44,800 --> 00:26:49,060
And my cousin is very cold and ignores people all day long.

365
00:26:49,060 --> 00:26:52,200
Whenever I eat there, I feel like I'll get indigestion.

366
00:26:52,200 --> 00:26:55,090
Especially my cousin, he...

367
00:26:56,940 --> 00:26:59,380
Let's not talk about him. Let's not talk about him.

368
00:26:59,380 --> 00:27:01,900
He is just very strange.

369
00:27:05,700 --> 00:27:09,360
This salad tastes better than the ones I ate abroad.

370
00:27:09,360 --> 00:27:10,690
- Really?
- Really!

371
00:27:10,690 --> 00:27:12,570
Then have some more.

372
00:27:14,900 --> 00:27:16,400
- You're lying.
- It's true.

373
00:27:16,400 --> 00:27:19,300
Hello, Embroiderer Wu. What is it?

374
00:27:19,300 --> 00:27:21,660
What happened? Tell me slowly.

375
00:27:23,630 --> 00:27:24,840
Lu Jun?

376
00:27:24,840 --> 00:27:27,170
Is everything okay with Master?

377
00:27:28,950 --> 00:27:31,600
Embroiderer Wu, don't worry. I will think of something.

378
00:27:31,600 --> 00:27:33,680
All right. Bye-bye.

379
00:27:39,210 --> 00:27:41,470
Mingxuan, it's so late yet you're still working?

380
00:27:41,470 --> 00:27:43,340
Mom, it's so late. You're still awake?

381
00:27:43,340 --> 00:27:46,420
I made this soup for you. Drink it while it's still hot.

382
00:27:46,420 --> 00:27:48,130
Thank you.

383
00:27:48,130 --> 00:27:51,980
Why hasn't Xueling come here lately?

384
00:27:52,860 --> 00:27:54,800
We are only colleagues.

385
00:27:54,800 --> 00:27:57,600
If there's something to talk about, we do it at the office.

386
00:27:57,600 --> 00:27:59,910
Why would she come here?

387
00:28:00,630 --> 00:28:04,000
Are you pretending not to understand or do you really not understand?

388
00:28:08,610 --> 00:28:10,840
I'm going to answer the phone.

389
00:28:13,460 --> 00:28:15,430
Hello, Mo Fei.

390
00:28:15,430 --> 00:28:17,520
Hello, President Tang. Do you have time tomorrow?

391
00:28:17,520 --> 00:28:20,160
Something has happened at the embroidery workshop.

392
00:28:22,150 --> 00:28:24,330
Last night, you mentioned a...

393
00:28:24,330 --> 00:28:27,660
Lu Jun. Who exactly is he?

394
00:28:27,660 --> 00:28:30,970
He is my master's nephew. He is extremely greedy.

395
00:28:30,970 --> 00:28:34,540
Each time the embroidery workshop makes money, he will come to ask for some.

396
00:28:34,540 --> 00:28:38,540
I don't know how he found out that the embroidery workshop is going to collaborate with Mingyuan.

397
00:28:38,540 --> 00:28:40,890
So, lately, he keeps pestering my master.

398
00:28:40,890 --> 00:28:44,530
He even took over a dozen relatives to my master's house yesterday.

399
00:28:44,530 --> 00:28:47,940
She had no choice but to hide.

400
00:28:49,670 --> 00:28:52,140
Have you seen him before?

401
00:28:52,140 --> 00:28:55,350
I have. What should we do now?

402
00:28:55,350 --> 00:28:58,620
Will the collaboration fall through now?

403
00:29:02,550 --> 00:29:04,670
Let's go see first.

404
00:29:07,410 --> 00:29:11,660
Whatever you want to talk about on behalf of Mingyuan, just talk to me.

405
00:29:11,660 --> 00:29:13,660
I make the decisions here.

406
00:29:13,660 --> 00:29:17,130
The price... is also decided by me.

407
00:29:18,050 --> 00:29:21,300
If you want to talk about a collaboration, then you should at least introduce yourself.

408
00:29:21,300 --> 00:29:23,400
I don't even know who you are.

409
00:29:23,400 --> 00:29:27,080
My name is Lu Jun. I am Master Li's nephew.

410
00:29:27,080 --> 00:29:30,160
I am also the legal person of this embroidery workshop.

411
00:29:30,160 --> 00:29:32,500
By the way, President Tang,

412
00:29:32,500 --> 00:29:35,410
my aunt already told me about

413
00:29:35,410 --> 00:29:37,270
your acquisition of the embroidery workshop.

414
00:29:37,270 --> 00:29:39,340
I can give you a reply right now.

415
00:29:39,340 --> 00:29:43,060
I don't agree to it.

416
00:29:45,260 --> 00:29:47,290
What's the reason?

417
00:29:47,950 --> 00:29:50,510
As for the reason–

418
00:29:50,510 --> 00:29:54,220
President Tang, what a coincidence.

419
00:29:54,220 --> 00:29:56,320
Long time no see.

420
00:29:57,180 --> 00:29:59,650
Here, Brother, have a seat.

421
00:30:02,810 --> 00:30:05,170
Who is this person?

422
00:30:10,820 --> 00:30:15,400
A supporting character. The bad guy.

423
00:30:16,710 --> 00:30:20,780
- Where's my aunt?
- Your aunt? She went out.

424
00:30:20,780 --> 00:30:24,590
Mister, who is your aunt?

425
00:30:25,330 --> 00:30:29,250
- Miss, who are you?
- She's your aunt's

426
00:30:29,250 --> 00:30:32,060
- apprentice.
- Apprentice?

427
00:30:32,060 --> 00:30:34,060
President Tang!

428
00:30:34,060 --> 00:30:38,070
Since you have already noticed, I might as well be honest with you.

429
00:30:38,070 --> 00:30:41,020
This embroidery workshop is our ancestral property.

430
00:30:41,020 --> 00:30:42,960
If you really want to buy it,

431
00:30:42,960 --> 00:30:46,000
then our whole family has to approve of it.

432
00:30:47,210 --> 00:30:52,250
So you mean that your family includes my competitor,

433
00:30:52,250 --> 00:30:54,480
President Zhu Haitian. Is that what you mean?

434
00:30:54,480 --> 00:30:57,810
President Tang, such a coincidence, such a coincidence.

435
00:30:59,070 --> 00:31:00,710
Wait!

436
00:31:00,710 --> 00:31:03,990
Why don't I understand this play you are acting out at all?

437
00:31:03,990 --> 00:31:06,050
Acting?

438
00:31:06,620 --> 00:31:10,110
What kind of play are we acting out? We are talking about business right now!

439
00:31:10,110 --> 00:31:14,710
So much effort just to discuss business. It must be hard on you guys.

440
00:31:15,620 --> 00:31:19,380
Malicious competition will only make the market worse and worse.

441
00:31:19,380 --> 00:31:22,910
Bettering the embroidery workshop relies on the passing down of the craftsmanship.

442
00:31:22,910 --> 00:31:26,950
Not on making a quick buck on an ancestral business like the two of you.

443
00:31:26,950 --> 00:31:32,170
President Tang, those words are a bit unpleasant to the ears.

444
00:31:33,610 --> 00:31:37,050
Do you deserve to have me talk nicely to you?

445
00:31:39,240 --> 00:31:43,270
Tang Mingxuan, aren't you too arrogant?

446
00:31:43,270 --> 00:31:46,290
Haiyao may lack the financial resources that

447
00:31:46,290 --> 00:31:48,270
Mingyuan has.

448
00:31:48,270 --> 00:31:50,740
But the capabilites of our clan

449
00:31:50,740 --> 00:31:53,020
are more than yours, aren't they?

450
00:31:53,020 --> 00:31:56,110
I have honestly not seen the capabilities you claim to have.

451
00:31:56,110 --> 00:31:58,840
But I really do admire your ability to boast.

452
00:31:58,840 --> 00:32:00,670
Hey, you!

453
00:32:03,050 --> 00:32:06,210
Let's go. It's not worth wasting our precious time on them.

454
00:32:06,210 --> 00:32:08,000
Let's go.

455
00:32:12,600 --> 00:32:14,280
Brother, how was that?

456
00:32:14,280 --> 00:32:16,700
Look at you!

457
00:32:18,000 --> 00:32:19,970
President Tang! President Tang!

458
00:32:19,970 --> 00:32:23,150
Wait, wait!

459
00:32:23,150 --> 00:32:25,670
Look! My younger brother is not very experienced.

460
00:32:25,670 --> 00:32:28,990
He doesn't know how to speak. He has offended you.

461
00:32:30,140 --> 00:32:33,910
President Tang, can we exchange a few words in private?

462
00:32:33,910 --> 00:32:36,140
Just for a bit.

463
00:32:37,270 --> 00:32:41,520
Based on our relationship, do you think that is appropriate?

464
00:32:41,520 --> 00:32:43,540
Look at the way you are talking.

465
00:32:43,540 --> 00:32:46,480
You two talk. I will wait for you outside.

466
00:32:46,480 --> 00:32:48,400
Thank you!

467
00:32:51,370 --> 00:32:54,410
President Tang, you have misunderstood me!

468
00:32:54,410 --> 00:32:58,480
Before I came here, I really didn't know about the situation between Mingyuan and the workshop.

469
00:32:58,480 --> 00:33:00,760
But now that I'm aware of it,

470
00:33:00,760 --> 00:33:02,550
as a gentleman, I have to help others fulfill their wish.

471
00:33:02,550 --> 00:33:04,960
With only one word of yours, the family's side...

472
00:33:04,960 --> 00:33:07,420
I will support you and be on your side, all right?

473
00:33:07,420 --> 00:33:10,330
Can you just be direct?

474
00:33:10,330 --> 00:33:12,940
Is what I'm saying not clear enough?

475
00:33:12,940 --> 00:33:15,050
I can help you with the acquisition of the embroidery workshop.

476
00:33:15,050 --> 00:33:17,070
Really, you might not believe it.

477
00:33:17,070 --> 00:33:18,750
Let me tell you.

478
00:33:18,750 --> 00:33:21,420
If I help you today, it's the same as helping my aunt.

479
00:33:21,420 --> 00:33:25,280
You probably know this better than I do. This embroidery workshop cannot survive for much longer.

480
00:33:25,280 --> 00:33:29,190
Although she's my maternal aunt, she is still a relative from the same clan.

481
00:33:29,190 --> 00:33:33,000
I can't just watch the embroidery workshop collapse, right?

482
00:33:33,770 --> 00:33:37,150
If you have any conditions, you can just say so directly.

483
00:33:37,150 --> 00:33:38,830
President Tang, you are insulting me.

484
00:33:38,830 --> 00:33:40,670
What conditions? There are no conditions.

485
00:33:40,670 --> 00:33:43,670
We are in the same industry so we run into each other all the time.

486
00:33:44,550 --> 00:33:47,380
Actually, I have always wanted to become friends with you.

487
00:33:47,380 --> 00:33:49,640
Since we're in the same industry, we're bound to collaborate.

488
00:33:49,640 --> 00:33:51,650
With you?

489
00:33:51,650 --> 00:33:53,440
Forget it.

490
00:33:54,890 --> 00:33:56,690
Wait! When did I

491
00:33:56,690 --> 00:33:59,810
ever offend you to make you so hostile towards me?

492
00:33:59,810 --> 00:34:03,050
Since you asked today, I will clear it up for you.

493
00:34:03,050 --> 00:34:07,150
Three years ago, did your company copy our design?

494
00:34:10,970 --> 00:34:12,080
That... Actually, that—

495
00:34:12,080 --> 00:34:16,730
When we sued you back then, the court also ruled you guys were guilty of plagiarizing.

496
00:34:16,730 --> 00:34:20,150
Yet you've only paid the fine. You never apologized.

497
00:34:20,150 --> 00:34:22,610
Do I need to say more?

498
00:34:22,610 --> 00:34:26,030
President Tang, this is old history. It has been three years.

499
00:34:26,030 --> 00:34:28,390
Let's both forget about this. Let's have tea,

500
00:34:28,390 --> 00:34:30,940
- and chat–
- Time has passed, but this matter cannot be in the past.

501
00:34:30,940 --> 00:34:35,190
As long as you don't apologize, there is no ending to this matter.

502
00:34:35,190 --> 00:34:40,860
Also, our company actually doesn't need a friend with no bottom line like you.

503
00:34:40,860 --> 00:34:43,000
In regards to our company's business,

504
00:34:44,300 --> 00:34:46,900
you don't need to worry.

505
00:34:48,270 --> 00:34:49,820
President Tang.

506
00:35:05,370 --> 00:35:10,410
Both Master Wu and Master Chen are not answering their phones. Where could they have gone?

